%h2
  Ruby on Rails Guides (#{@edge ? @version[0, 7] : @version})
- if @edge
  %p
    These are
    = succeed "," do
      %b Edge Guides
    %a{:href => "https://github.com/rails/rails/tree/#{@version}"} master
    branch.
  %p
    If you are looking for the ones for the stable version, please check
    %a{:href => "http://guides.rubyonrails.org"} http://guides.rubyonrails.org
    instead.
- else
  %p
    These are the new guides for Rails 4.2 based on
    = succeed "." do
      %a{:href => "https://github.com/rails/rails/tree/#{@version}"}= @version
%p
  The guides for earlier releases:
  = succeed "," do
    %a{:href => "http://guides.rubyonrails.org/v4.1/"} Rails 4.1
  = succeed "," do
    %a{:href => "http://guides.rubyonrails.org/v4.0/"} Rails 4.0
  = succeed "," do
    %a{:href => "http://guides.rubyonrails.org/v3.2/"} Rails 3.2
  = succeed "." do
    %a{:href => "http://guides.rubyonrails.org/v2.3/"} Rails 2.3
